  "text": "Found 7 deprecated DataStream API classes in Apache Flink (github.com/sg-evals/flink--0cc95fcc) under flink-streaming-java/src/. These include source functions, sink functions, timestamp extractors, and I/O format classes:\n\n1. TextInputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink.\n\n2. TextOutputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink.\n\n3. AscendingTimestampExtractor (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - Deprecated timestamp extractor for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No replacement specified in javadoc.\n\n4. DiscardingSink (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/legacy/DiscardingSink.java) - Deprecated sink that ignores all elements. Recommended replacement: org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.sink.v2.DiscardingSink.\n\n5. DataGeneratorSource (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/source/datagen/DataGeneratorSource.java) - Deprecated data generator source function. Recommended replacement: org.apache.flink.connector.datagen.source.DataGeneratorSource.\n\n6. TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/legacy/TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction.java) - Deprecated base class for exactly-once semantic sink functions using two-phase commit. Recommended replacement: org.apache.flink.api.connector.sink2.Sink.\n\n7. StreamingFileSink (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/filesystem/legacy/StreamingFileSink.java) - Deprecated sink for writing to file systems with bucket support. Recommended replacement: org.apache.flink.connector.file.sink.FileSink."
}

